{"tid":2021493,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣....","createTime":"2020-05-17T18:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T16:37:22.000Z","uid":208097,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"509326945095696d4b34586796d85f9be77893ec","tid":2021493,"uid":208097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T18:34:14.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人同我發同一個夢.喺個夢到比人拉咗.被控罪名係暴動.就嚟踏入二字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過已經諗過將來要點.我已經煩惱緊上court着咩衫好.平時唔使翻工嘅時候盡量見下朋友.有時佢哋都會問做咩無啦啦嚟見我吖.我會答想見你咪嚟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話雖如此,但其實我發覺呢刻再唔珍惜呢種冇任何嘢阻隔嘅距離.遲啲一定會後悔.我已經決定咗上庭嘅時間地點唔會同任何人講.我諗入到去都未必會想見任何人.幸好我宜家仲係隻單身狗.唔洗連累到其他人.<br />\n一到夜晚就好多嘢諗.莫怪我同p仔冇差別<br />\n最後都係嗰句.有咩做到就做啦.黃色經濟圈難唔到大家的.做下慈善活動.捐下錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係會幫到好多人架."},{"pid":"3a832622bea9fd5dde645e473238825027aa5906","tid":2021493,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"566341b5c2cc630b5415788ddd6f3b76c0c0f337","tid":2021493,"uid":241643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />I know that feel"},{"pid":"5a386e277a2745a7a2e89db399b77da944dfea2f","tid":2021493,"uid":242110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:37:22.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hk